<sect1 id="REALFORMAT">
  <!-- DNT-Start --><title>REALFORMAT<indexterm>
      <primary>REALFORMAT</primary>
    </indexterm></title><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para><emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->REALFORMAT<!-- DNT-End --><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->REALFORMAT<!-- DNT-End --> Function</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis><emphasis>expression, width, decimals
  </emphasis><emphasis role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <para><informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colwidth="78.45pt" />

        <colspec colwidth="274.35pt" />

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis>expression</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry>The expression that specifies the <!-- DNT-Start -->REAL<!-- DNT-End --> value to
            format.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis>width</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry>The size of string in which to right-justify the
            value.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis>decimals</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry>An integer specifying the number of decimal places.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->Return:<!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->REALFORMAT<!-- DNT-End --> returns a single value.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable></para>

  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->REALFORMAT<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>function returns the
  value of the <emphasis>expression</emphasis> formatted as a right-justified
  string of <emphasis>width</emphasis> characters with the number of
  <emphasis>decimals</emphasis> specifed.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting>REAL8 Float := 1000.0063;
STRING12 FloatStr12 := REALFORMAT(float,12,6);
OUTPUT(FloatStr12); //results in ' 1000.006300'</programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para>See Also: <link linkend="INTFORMAT"><!-- DNT-Start -->INTFORMAT<!-- DNT-End --></link></para>
</sect1>
